qt_version

Returns Qt version used.

Syntax

v = qt_version()

Output argument

v

a string : valid path.

Description

v = qt_version() returns the version number of Qt at run-time as a string (for example, "5.15.2").

Example

semver(qt_version(), '>5.15')

See also

semver.

History

Version Description
1.0.0 initial version
